1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,980
= Episode 36 =

20
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:53,940
Have you checked Winehouse Fan?

21
00:01:57,220 --> 00:01:58,420
I know that place.

22
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:01,220
The No.1 restaurant in town

23
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:03,940
is unable to pay the tax due to great deficits

24
00:02:03,940 --> 00:02:05,460
and has to sell its property.

25
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:07,260
It’s big news in the city.

26
00:02:07,740 --> 00:02:09,740
The Agency ought to look into it.

27
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:12,460
All the details are in my monthly report

28
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:13,540
to Officer Ren.

29
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:16,980
He said

30
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:19,220
Deputy Officer Yang had told him about it

31
00:02:20,020 --> 00:02:21,460
and the investigation was ongoing.

32
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:38,380
Your Majesty, please take the sedan chair.

33
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:41,580
Get to the bottom of it.

34
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:43,500
Find out everything about the merchant

35
00:02:43,860 --> 00:02:44,780
who colluded with the owner

36
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:46,420
to buy that place at a low price.

37
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:47,820
Yes.

38
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:48,980
Also, figure out

39
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:51,500
who’s going to take over that place.

40
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:11,980
Aunt.

41
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:27,460
Now what?

42
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:32,540
You won’t even serve me tea?

43
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:35,860
Please forgive me.

44
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,740
I...I’m only a humble maid.

45
00:03:39,180 --> 00:03:40,020
I never expected

46
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:42,100
that I’d have the honor to serve you tea.

47
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:43,860
I’m flattered

48
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,220
and a bit overwhelmed.

49
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:52,500
I already make you flattered?

50
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:56,220
I planned

51
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:59,300
to have you serve someone else.

52
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,980
But you might not be up for the job.

53
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:04,660
Never mind.

54
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:08,180
I could.

55
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:09,580
I can do it.

56
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:15,420
Madam Zhang is still weak.

57
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:18,500
If I have the honor to look after her,

58
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,980
I’ll do my best

59
00:04:20,140 --> 00:04:21,260
and attend to her every need.

60
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:41,780
Aunt.

61
00:04:43,740 --> 00:04:44,860
Do you want me

62
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:47,420
to replace her to serve His Majesty?

63
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,060
I assume

64
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:58,460
you’ve been longing for that chance.

65
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:02,380
Yes. That’s my dream,

66
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:04,060
but doesn’t every woman in this palace

67
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:05,700
dream of the same thing?

68
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:10,940
How could I

69
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:14,140
let an ambitious woman

70
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,860
approach His Majesty

71
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:18,460
when Madam Zhang is sick?

72
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:23,260
I’ll be honest with you.

73
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:25,820
Were it a few years back,

74
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,900
I might...

75
00:05:28,540 --> 00:05:30,300
I might still have hope.

76
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:32,220
But now,

77
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:34,380
seeing how His Majesty treats her every day,

78
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:36,220
how could I not give up?

79
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:40,060
Only with her help

80
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,820
and trust,

81
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:43,340
will I be able to assist her

82
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,220
when she’s in need

83
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,140
and have the chance

84
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:47,180
to be praised by His Majesty.

85
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:51,020
Helping her...is helping myself.

86
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:52,860
Harming her is harming myself.

87
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:05,340
I hope

88
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,660
you’ll forever remember that.

89
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,580
I will.

90
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:14,300
Don’t harm yourself and others.

91
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:31,460
Monks are chanting the sutra.

92
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:33,300
For whom?

93
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,340
The Third Prince passed away.

94
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:41,300
Lady Zhu’s son Xi’er?

95
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:43,500
Yes.

96
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:50,460
He’d be two years old next month.

97
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:52,380
His Majesty

98
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:54,500
also planned to promote Lady Zhu.

99
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:56,420
Unexpectedly,

100
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:58,140
her son caught a cold and had a fever.

101
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:00,700
He died in two days.

102
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:04,340
His death isn’t alone.

103
00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:09,900
Two months ago, Lady Shiping’s daughter

104
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:12,140
didn’t survive the first two hours
after she was born.

105
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:14,900
Clearly,

106
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:17,220
you’re blessed by heaven.

107
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,900
The Eighth Princess didn’t arrive too smoothly,

108
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:23,540
but in the end, you’re both safe.

109
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:27,500
Where’s her?

110
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:30,780
Don’t worry.

111
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:33,340
She’s fed and sleeping now.

112
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:34,700
She’s fine.

113
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:35,820
When she wakes up,

114
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:37,060
I’ll bring her to you.

115
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:38,980
By the way,

116
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:41,900
His Majesty named her this morning.

117
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:46,860
He woke up

118
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:48,140
while you were still asleep.

119
00:07:48,580 --> 00:07:49,860
Then the Eighth Princess was up too,

120
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:51,260
so I brought her to him.

121
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,820
She was so sweet

122
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:56,580
that she didn’t cry in His Majesty’s arms.

123
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:58,220
He adored her.

124
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:01,500
Then he carried her to the window.

125
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:03,100
When she heard

126
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:05,340
the monks chanting the sutra,

127
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:07,380
her eyes started to roll

128
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:10,300
as if she was interested in it.

129
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,540
So

130
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:13,500
His Majesty gave her a name.

131
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:17,140
“Call her Youwu then”.

132
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:22,340
May Yaoyao and Youwu

133
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:24,900
be safe

134
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:26,580
and healthy.

135
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:40,140
I’m constantly tired lately.

136
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,940
It’s been almost a month since I gave birth

137
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:44,980
but I can hardly get out of bed.

138
00:08:46,780 --> 00:08:48,260
Out of 24 hours a day,

139
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,740
I’m only awake

140
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:53,060
for less than four hours.

141
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:57,020
Didn’t the Imperial Physicians say

142
00:08:57,460 --> 00:09:00,340
it takes time for you to recover?

143
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,420
Take it easy. I’m here with you.

144
00:09:02,580 --> 00:09:03,700
Go to sleep if you’re tired.

145
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:05,660
I’ll keep an eye

146
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,340
on your two daughters.

147
00:09:08,540 --> 00:09:09,700
Over the past few days,

148
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:13,220
I didn’t even know

149
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,060
when His Majesty arrived.

150
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:16,500
In the past,

151
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:18,300
it was you

152
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:19,820
who handled His Majesty’s daily routine.

153
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:22,140
Today, after he woke up,

154
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:24,260
I...I dared not

155
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,460
handle it for him

156
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:27,260
in case he’d be uncomfortable.

157
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:28,340
But...

158
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:30,700
But after looking around,

159
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:32,940
no one was fit for the job,

160
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:36,100
so I went to the utility room

161
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:38,660
to fetch Lantiao to do it.

162
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:51,460
Madam,

163
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:57,380
you still need more rest.

164
00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:00,660
His Majesty cares about you

165
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:02,980
and comes to visit you every day.

166
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:04,180
If...

167
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:06,340
there’s no one to serve him

168
00:10:06,820 --> 00:10:08,460
and you fall asleep,

169
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:10,980
he’ll probably leave.

170
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:13,460
If he doesn’t go back to his own chamber,

171
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:15,900
he’s most likely

172
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:17,300
to go to Madam Miao’s.

173
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:18,660
I’m thinking

174
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:20,180
if we need

175
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:21,780
a good-looking

176
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,220
and astute maid.

177
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:26,460
Aunt, did you just say

178
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:28,900
it was Lantiao

179
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:30,420
who served His Majesty this morning?

180
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:35,700
I...I...

181
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:38,180
I had no choice.

182
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:40,660
She...she’s mediocre

183
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:43,060
and plain-looking.

184
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:44,460
Let her work inside.

185
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:49,260
Before I recover,

186
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:53,020
she can serve His Majesty for me.

187
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:14,500
Your Majesty, Zhang Maoze is outside.

188
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:24,700
Send him in.

189
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,740
Yuansheng, the adopted son of the landlady

190
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:39,780
of Restaurant of Breeze, is busy

191
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:42,180
raising money to pay Winehouse Fan’s tax.

192
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:45,380
You may still remember him.

193
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:48,020
When he was young,

194
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:49,700
he managed to expose his aunt’s affair

195
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:51,660
and theft of his family’s property.

196
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:53,540
Then he was enlisted in the army

197
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:55,620
and contributed the most to exonerating Mr. Liu

198
00:11:55,780 --> 00:11:57,740
in Liu Ping and Huang Dehe’s case.

199
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:04,620
There’s something...

200
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:07,620
I didn’t tell you before.

201
00:12:09,460 --> 00:12:11,140
I didn’t mean to hide it from you, though.

202
00:12:12,420 --> 00:12:13,620
Yuansheng is a Liang.

203
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:16,940
He’s the Liang family’s child.

204
00:12:23,900 --> 00:12:24,740
I’m guilty.

205
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:27,140
I knew it for long

206
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:28,820
but didn’t know how to bring it up.

207
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:33,380
I know you’ve kept the joss paper

208
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:35,340
used during the Liang family’s funeral

209
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:36,220
and you...

210
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:37,620
I was aware

211
00:12:40,820 --> 00:12:43,780
of his background

212
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:45,180
when he was sent to the army.

213
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:48,940
I understand

214
00:12:50,340 --> 00:12:51,660
your concern.

215
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:00,940
All these years...

216
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:04,540
All these years,

217
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:07,500
you know

218
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:10,060
that not a day goes by

219
00:13:10,060 --> 00:13:12,220
that my guilt for mother is lessened.

220
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,500
I can’t even think of her

221
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,340
or pay her respects in person.

222
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,380
After learning of Yuansheng’s background,

223
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:25,220
I actually envied him.

224
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:30,020
He could avenge his mother’s death

225
00:13:30,300 --> 00:13:31,860
and bring the sinners to justice.

226
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:33,780
How wonderful!

227
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:37,180
So what if he violated the law

228
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:38,340
and was sentenced to military duty?

229
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:39,660
I bet

230
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:42,620
he could live with a clear conscience.

231
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:47,500
Your Majesty can’t be selfish.

232
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:49,780
Your burden is too heavy.

233
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:54,220
Had I

234
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:56,060
insisted on visiting my mother,

235
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:57,540
what would the Empress Dowager have done?

236
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:00,780
Dethrone me?

237
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:03,700
Harm my mother or jeopardize state affairs?

238
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:04,460
Would she?

239
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,460
What about the state?

240
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,020
What about the people?

241
00:14:23,180 --> 00:14:24,340
Over the past decades,

242
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,660
I’ve had so many worries and concerns.

243
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:28,940
I dare not cross the line,

244
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,780
or love or hate anyone freely.

245
00:14:31,940 --> 00:14:33,140
Still, there were earthquakes

246
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:34,580
and snow disasters.

247
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:35,260
Still,

248
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:37,060
thousands of people died.

249
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:41,620
Why? What does heaven want from me?

250
00:14:58,700 --> 00:14:59,660
Do you know

251
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:06,780
uncle held my hands in his sickbed

252
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,940
and said the series of deaths of my children

253
00:15:11,540 --> 00:15:12,420
could be caused

254
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:15,220
by my failure to look after my mother.

255
00:15:18,140 --> 00:15:20,300
Back then, he risked his life to tell me

256
00:15:21,380 --> 00:15:23,820
my birth mother’s location and condition

257
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:27,660
just so I could fulfill my duty as a son

258
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:29,740
to call her mother and look after her.

259
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:35,020
But I didn’t visit her.

260
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:39,100
I continued

261
00:15:39,420 --> 00:15:41,860
to be obedient to the Empress Dowager

262
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:45,900
and I even pretended

263
00:15:49,020 --> 00:15:50,380
not to know my mother’s death.

264
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:55,500
Your Majesty.

265
00:15:57,900 --> 00:15:58,620
Your Majesty.

266
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:01,620
I know I could be killed by judging a prince,

267
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:03,820
but I have to say this.

268
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:07,060
Your Majesty, as you know,

269
00:16:08,380 --> 00:16:10,700
the Eighth Prince detests
Empress Dowager Zhangxian.

270
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:12,940
He might’ve told you the secret

271
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:15,180
out of ulterior motives.

272
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:16,460
And he brought up the past again

273
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:18,780
probably out of personal grudge.

274
00:16:22,340 --> 00:16:23,340
He said

275
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:26,580
Mr. Yan had known the truth

276
00:16:27,980 --> 00:16:29,540
but he dared not leave any record

277
00:16:29,540 --> 00:16:30,500
on my mother’s stone tablet.

278
00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:32,460
Uncle called him the Empress Dowager’s flunky,

279
00:16:34,860 --> 00:16:36,700
saying appointing him prime minister

280
00:16:38,460 --> 00:16:40,300
was a betrayal of my mother

281
00:16:41,060 --> 00:16:42,260
and against heaven’s will.

282
00:16:44,260 --> 00:16:45,140
Prime Minister Yan

283
00:16:45,580 --> 00:16:46,740
was demoted repeatedly

284
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:49,100
for disagreeing with the Empress Dowager.

285
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:50,700
The Eighth Prince is in critical condition

286
00:16:51,180 --> 00:16:53,740
and obsessed with divination and astrology.

287
00:16:54,460 --> 00:16:55,380
I’m afraid...

288
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:02,620
I know you respect him

289
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,980
and don’t want to argue with him,

290
00:17:05,340 --> 00:17:06,380
but you shouldn’t

291
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:09,580
bother yourself with his complaints.

292
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:15,340
By divination or astrology,

293
00:17:18,020 --> 00:17:20,140
who can tell me

294
00:17:21,860 --> 00:17:23,300
heaven’s will?

295
00:17:27,700 --> 00:17:28,980
If I know that,

296
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:33,020
I’m willing to be punished

297
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:34,420
by heaven for the state

298
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:37,300
and the people.

299
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:42,820
Why did it take away my children?

300
00:17:50,540 --> 00:17:52,140
Who can tell me

301
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:56,420
how to

302
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:00,260
follow heaven’s will?

303
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:16,860
You each hold

304
00:18:16,860 --> 00:18:17,820
a windproof lantern.

305
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:19,940
Take care of the princess on the way.

306
00:18:23,060 --> 00:18:23,780
Your Highness,

307
00:18:23,820 --> 00:18:25,060
why aren’t you going to visit father

308
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:26,020
with me?

309
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:28,140
When you

310
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,980
are with your father alone,

311
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:31,500
you can be more relaxed

312
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:32,620
to cheer him up.

313
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:35,340
I don’t think

314
00:18:36,260 --> 00:18:37,580
I’m a good comforter.

315
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:41,380
Due to Liang Yuansheng’s contribution

316
00:18:41,380 --> 00:18:42,260
in Liu Ping’s case,

317
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:44,780
I remember he was rewarded handsomely.

318
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:46,100
What happened afterwards?

319
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:49,500
He followed Prime Minister Han to Shaanxi,

320
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:50,860
and then Prime Minister Han recommended him

321
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:52,380
to General Di Qing before his transfer.

322
00:18:53,060 --> 00:18:54,180
Yuansheng worked undercover in Xixia for a year

323
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:56,740
and successfully incited the revolt there.

324
00:18:57,260 --> 00:18:58,740
Somehow,

325
00:18:58,940 --> 00:18:59,940
he only claimed the prize

326
00:18:59,940 --> 00:19:01,100
but turned down the promotion.

327
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:03,380
Perhaps he’s really into business.

328
00:19:06,260 --> 00:19:07,820
What about Merchant Chen

329
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:09,740
and the former owner of Winehouse Fan?

330
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:13,060
They did have connections with Prime Minister Jia,

331
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:14,460
but they were discreet.

332
00:19:14,660 --> 00:19:16,780
Prime Minister Jia’s butler served
as the middleman.

333
00:19:17,669 --> 00:19:18,302
And...

334
00:19:19,580 --> 00:19:21,580
And Xia Song was involved in it, too.

335
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,460
I’ve acquired evidence

336
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:26,540
of Prime Minister Jia profiting from it

337
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:28,740
and still working on Chief Xia’s case.

338
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:31,140
There are some clues but no concrete evidence.

339
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:47,940
You mean Yuansheng was raising money himself?

340
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:49,380
Han Qi didn’t help him?

341
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:51,820
Not that I know of.

342
00:19:56,460 --> 00:19:58,260
Take money from my savings

343
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,740
to make up the gap.

344
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,340
Invest it into Winehouse Fan in your name.

345
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:04,180
Remember, don’t tell him it’s a loan.

346
00:20:04,420 --> 00:20:06,020
You’re only investing in his business

347
00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:06,980
to get returns.

348
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,300
He’ll be reluctant

349
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:11,980
but given your posts

350
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:13,380
in the Bureau and the Agency,

351
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:14,980
he won’t turn you down.

352
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:18,740
Your Majesty is thorough.

353
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,100
If we lend him

354
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:21,380
so much money all of a sudden,

355
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:23,180
he’d surely get suspicious.

356
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:24,700
It’s no secret

357
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:26,940
that eunuchs are greedy
and love buying properties.

358
00:20:27,140 --> 00:20:28,540
It all makes sense.

359
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,540
With my status

360
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:32,060
and investment in his business,

361
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:34,620
others won’t dare to sabotage it.

362
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:37,500
Killing more birds with one stone. Brilliant!

363
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:43,180
Nature has its own laws.

364
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:45,940
They didn’t benefit Emperor Yao

365
00:20:47,300 --> 00:20:48,700
or harm King Jie.

366
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:52,700
Obey the laws, the nation will thrive.

367
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:55,300
Disobey the law, chaos will arise.

368
00:20:56,660 --> 00:20:58,620
I received another report from men in the Agency

369
00:20:58,780 --> 00:20:59,780
that I think

370
00:20:59,820 --> 00:21:02,220
Your Majesty should know.

371
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:03,540
What is it about?

372
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:04,900
Building Shuiluo City.

373
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:07,220
Prime Minister Han called it off.

374
00:21:07,420 --> 00:21:08,420
After he was called back to the Capital,

375
00:21:08,460 --> 00:21:10,660
his successor Chief Zheng supported
the construction.

376
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:16,780
If it can be built,

377
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:19,420
it’ll strengthen the security of the border.

378
00:21:20,300 --> 00:21:23,340
But it’s a minority community.

379
00:21:23,380 --> 00:21:24,380
Situations there are complicated.

380
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:25,460
The construction is not easy.

381
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:29,580
Although Han Qi and Zheng Jian

382
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:31,380
disagree with each other

383
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:32,980
for the sake of the state,

384
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:36,300
I don’t think so.

385
00:21:37,540 --> 00:21:39,340
They may have a conflict of interest,

386
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:40,740
but General Liu Hu

387
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:43,220
managed to complete it.

388
00:21:44,780 --> 00:21:46,100
A low-ranking general

389
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:47,420
accomplished the task

390
00:21:47,420 --> 00:21:48,500
that Han Qi and Zheng Jian failed?

391
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:51,300
Liu Hu’s talent

392
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:52,820
is no match for those two,

393
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:54,380
but he’s stationed there long enough

394
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:56,940
to know the terrain and the people better.

395
00:21:57,580 --> 00:21:59,620
Also, the minorities agreed to give him the land,

396
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:01,460
so Liu Hu decided

397
00:22:01,460 --> 00:22:03,340
to finish the construction.

398
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:05,140
That was the right decision.

399
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:06,140
The thing is,

400
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:08,220
Prime Minister Han already stopped it.

401
00:22:08,820 --> 00:22:10,220
According to the law,

402
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,380
Chief Zheng

403
00:22:11,420 --> 00:22:13,620
is unable to overrule a prime minister’s decision.

404
00:22:17,620 --> 00:22:18,420
Dig deeper.

405
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:20,620
If Liu Hu

406
00:22:20,620 --> 00:22:22,220
can convince the minorities to give up the land,

407
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:23,740
I can issue a follow-up decree.

408
00:22:24,740 --> 00:22:25,460
Two days ago,

409
00:22:25,460 --> 00:22:26,740
Governor Yin Zhu of Wei County

410
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:29,180
dispatched General Di Qing to Shuiluo City

411
00:22:29,500 --> 00:22:31,620
to arrest General Liu

412
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:33,940
for disobeying Prime Minister Han’s order.

413
00:22:34,780 --> 00:22:37,740
What? He ordered Di Qing to make an arrest?

414
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:42,380
No action was taken before,

415
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:43,700
but right after Liu Hu

416
00:22:43,780 --> 00:22:44,980
convinced them to give up the land,

417
00:22:44,980 --> 00:22:45,860
he got arrested.

418
00:22:46,820 --> 00:22:47,740
That Yin Zhu

419
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:49,820
is so narrow-minded.

420
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:54,140
No.

421
00:23:00,380 --> 00:23:01,420
I get it.

422
00:23:03,300 --> 00:23:05,180
Zheng Jian reported Teng Zongliang.

423
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:07,300
Yin Zhu is Ouyang Xiu

424
00:23:07,300 --> 00:23:08,460
and Fan Zhongyan’s friend,

425
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:10,300
so he’s against Zheng Jian.

426
00:23:10,860 --> 00:23:12,180
Zheng Jian supports Liu Hu,

427
00:23:12,180 --> 00:23:13,140
so Yin Zhu is targeting at Liu Hu

428
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,220
to stop him from making any achievement.

429
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:18,420
That’s a so-called gentleman.

430
00:23:26,620 --> 00:23:27,940
Teng Zongliang and Liu Hu

431
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:29,540
are loyal officials

432
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:31,260
but they broke the law.

433
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:32,980
Groups they’re in

434
00:23:33,260 --> 00:23:34,660
are rivals in court.

435
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:38,340
Right now, one is imprisoned in Binzhou

436
00:23:38,740 --> 00:23:40,220
while the other is sent to the Capital.

437
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:46,180
How ironically fair!

438
00:23:47,860 --> 00:23:49,700
Father, are you in the study?

439
00:23:57,580 --> 00:23:58,460
It’s cold.

440
00:23:58,700 --> 00:24:00,140
What are you doing here?

441
00:24:01,580 --> 00:24:02,500
Starting from today,

442
00:24:02,860 --> 00:24:04,980
I won’t use braziers here.

443
00:24:05,780 --> 00:24:06,540
I knew

444
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:07,940
you stopped using them

445
00:24:08,180 --> 00:24:08,980
and eating dinner,

446
00:24:09,340 --> 00:24:11,140
so I came to join you.

447
00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:14,460
Oh, I’ve had dinner today.

448
00:24:14,820 --> 00:24:15,620
Starting from tomorrow then.

449
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:17,220
Nonsense!

450
00:24:18,100 --> 00:24:19,460
You’re doing it yourself.

451
00:24:19,820 --> 00:24:21,140
How could it be nonsense?

452
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:24,820
I have my responsibility.

453
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:26,420
You’re a child.

454
00:24:27,100 --> 00:24:30,100
I’m also your eldest daughter and a princess.

455
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:31,540
It’s also my responsibility

456
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:33,340
to share your burden

457
00:24:33,620 --> 00:24:34,620
even if I can’t do much.

458
00:24:37,340 --> 00:24:37,980
Father,

459
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,020
I was reciting

460
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:40,940
an extremely long article.

461
00:24:41,340 --> 00:24:42,460
It took me two days

462
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:43,740
to remember every word.

463
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:48,300
And here I am to collect my prize.

464
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:51,300
An extremely long article?

465
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:52,580
What is it

466
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:54,380
that you volunteered

467
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:55,620
to recite it?

468
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:56,980
I don’t believe it.

469
00:24:57,540 --> 00:24:58,540
This one is different.

470
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:01,340
It spoke to me the moment I read it.

471
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:03,660
What is it about?

472
00:25:07,060 --> 00:25:08,380
Nature has its own laws.

473
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:11,780
They didn’t benefit Emperor Yao or harm King Jie.

474
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:26,780
I heard the former Chief of Shaanxi

475
00:25:26,780 --> 00:25:27,620
Zheng Jian

476
00:25:27,700 --> 00:25:28,900
accused Teng Zongliang

477
00:25:29,060 --> 00:25:31,140
of misusing public funds.

478
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:33,940
Investigating Censor Liang Jian reported

479
00:25:34,220 --> 00:25:36,500
that the number reached 160,000.

480
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:37,580
Sir.

481
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:38,780
- Have some tea. - Had I known less

482
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:41,260
about Zongliang

483
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,820
or military affairs

484
00:25:44,300 --> 00:25:45,420
in Qing County and Wei County,

485
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:48,940
I would’ve been shocked and furious

486
00:25:49,380 --> 00:25:52,500
and demanded severe punishments.

487
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:56,460
But I was well aware of the military expense

488
00:25:56,660 --> 00:25:57,860
and the allocation of money there...

489
00:26:02,060 --> 00:26:02,860
Father.

490
00:26:04,380 --> 00:26:05,180
Father?

491
00:26:05,780 --> 00:26:06,900
Did I make any mistake?

492
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:11,300
What made you

493
00:26:11,300 --> 00:26:12,580
recite Xuncius’s article?

494
00:26:13,340 --> 00:26:14,460
Teachers in the palace

495
00:26:14,780 --> 00:26:15,980
don’t cover his works.

496
00:26:17,100 --> 00:26:18,100
You once said

497
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:22,060
Emperor Yao was an almighty ruler.

498
00:26:22,820 --> 00:26:24,180
As mighty as he was,

499
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:26,740
he wasn’t entitled to enjoy extreme pleasure

500
00:26:27,380 --> 00:26:28,780
or supremacy

501
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:30,900
but had to shoulder the responsibility

502
00:26:30,900 --> 00:26:32,580
much greater than others’.

503
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:37,060
I’m proud of you.

504
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:40,060
You still remember

505
00:26:40,060 --> 00:26:41,340
the story

506
00:26:41,740 --> 00:26:42,940
that I told you long ago.

507
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:44,580
I do.

508
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:47,140
Back then, I asked you

509
00:26:47,900 --> 00:26:49,340
why you didn’t get rid of the quilt

510
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:50,860
whose color already faded

511
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,340
after being washed so many times.

512
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:54,500
You practically own the state.

513
00:26:55,100 --> 00:26:56,740
Why were you so frugal?

514
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:59,700
Then you told me Emperor Yao’s story.

515
00:27:00,540 --> 00:27:01,620
You said

516
00:27:01,980 --> 00:27:04,100
you’d never be half as great as he was,

517
00:27:04,740 --> 00:27:07,060
but every emperor should learn from the sage

518
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:09,300
about how to be a great emperor.

519
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:14,180
How to be a great emperor?

520
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,380
How to be a great emperor?

521
00:27:53,100 --> 00:27:54,420
Clear things up.

522
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:56,020
Once we get out of the mountain,

523
00:27:56,260 --> 00:27:57,820
we’ll stay the night in the town ahead.

524
00:27:58,540 --> 00:27:59,220
Yes.

525
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:00,820
Come here and move these things away.

526
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:02,100
Hurry!

527
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:08,140
Here.

528
00:28:10,300 --> 00:28:11,500
= Liu Hu, courtesy name Zijun =

529
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:13,340
Thank you for treating me so well on the way.

530
00:28:14,460 --> 00:28:15,180
General Di,

531
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,220
I admire you the most

532
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:19,580
among all the generals in the west.

533
00:28:24,060 --> 00:28:24,780
Today,

534
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:27,060
I want you to be honest with me.

535
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:29,900
Should Shuiluo City be built or not?

536
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,580
Isn’t it an important military base?

537
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:34,940
I worked tirelessly

538
00:28:34,980 --> 00:28:36,300
to gain the land

539
00:28:36,820 --> 00:28:37,820
and cooperate with the minorities.

540
00:28:38,380 --> 00:28:39,740
Isn’t it beneficial to the state?

541
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:43,300
If everyone acts like you

542
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:44,820
and disobeys orders,

543
00:28:44,980 --> 00:28:45,900
how could the troops be disciplined?

544
00:28:46,860 --> 00:28:47,780
General Di,

545
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:49,580
on the battlefield,

546
00:28:51,620 --> 00:28:52,900
when your superior

547
00:28:53,140 --> 00:28:53,860
gives you an order from the base

548
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:55,500
that’s made based on false information,

549
00:28:56,100 --> 00:28:57,260
you’re at the front line

550
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:58,780
and know things have changed.

551
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:00,180
This order

552
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:03,580
will cost you the chance to win, your men’s lives

553
00:29:03,860 --> 00:29:04,780
and the future of the state,

554
00:29:05,700 --> 00:29:08,300
will you follow it or not?

555
00:29:09,780 --> 00:29:10,540
Besides,

556
00:29:11,060 --> 00:29:12,300
in terms of building Shuiluo City,

557
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:14,860
I’m not sure

558
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:17,780
if I really disobeyed the order.

559
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:19,820
I know

560
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:22,020
when Prime Minister Han was in charge,

561
00:29:22,980 --> 00:29:24,780
he forbade us from building it.

562
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:27,500
At that time, we lost the battle at Haoshuichuan.

563
00:29:27,860 --> 00:29:29,020
Our morale was impaired.

564
00:29:29,540 --> 00:29:30,620
The minorities weren’t afraid of us.

565
00:29:31,420 --> 00:29:32,780
When things came round,

566
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:35,220
Prime Minister Han had left for another post.

567
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:39,180
When Provincial Governor and Chief Zheng Jian

568
00:29:39,620 --> 00:29:40,540
arrived for inspection,

569
00:29:40,860 --> 00:29:42,260
I tried to convince him.

570
00:29:43,060 --> 00:29:44,460
After thorough inspections,

571
00:29:44,780 --> 00:29:46,100
he agreed to the construction.

572
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:48,620
You’re playing dumb there.

573
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:50,780
Zheng Jian no longer governed Wei County.

574
00:29:51,300 --> 00:29:52,420
You were directly answering

575
00:29:52,420 --> 00:29:54,100
to Governor Yin Zhu.

576
00:29:54,860 --> 00:29:56,460
Chief Zheng, the former governor,

577
00:29:57,020 --> 00:29:58,540
overreached himself

578
00:29:58,540 --> 00:29:59,420
into someone else’s jurisdiction

579
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:01,300
and helped you with the construction.

580
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:03,420
He was treating Governor Yin with disdain.

581
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:05,700
General Liu,

582
00:30:06,660 --> 00:30:08,140
this isn’t your first day at work.

583
00:30:08,780 --> 00:30:09,940
I don’t believe you know nothing about it.

584
00:30:11,140 --> 00:30:12,540
I don’t care who I answer to

585
00:30:13,180 --> 00:30:15,860
as long as he agrees to let me build the city.

586
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:18,180
I can give him

587
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:19,460
my life.

588
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:23,540
Please do your best to lobby court officials.

589
00:30:24,540 --> 00:30:25,540
Anyone is fine.

590
00:30:26,060 --> 00:30:28,420
Shuiluo City cannot be abandoned.

591
00:30:33,780 --> 00:30:37,580
I’m willing to die for my mistake

592
00:30:38,580 --> 00:30:39,820
but that city is innocent

593
00:30:40,340 --> 00:30:41,140
and so are

594
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:43,340
the Hans and minorities there.

595
00:30:45,580 --> 00:30:49,140
Please kill me but continue the construction.

596
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:03,460
Father, you’re worried about others all night,

597
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:06,340
giving them free rice

598
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:09,180
and selling them coal at a low price.

599
00:31:10,740 --> 00:31:14,660
Don’t…don’t skip your meal.

600
00:31:23,780 --> 00:31:25,900
I have desserts in my bag.

601
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:29,220
Please have some.

602
00:31:30,820 --> 00:31:32,140
Just one.

603
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:03,260
Huirou,

604
00:32:05,540 --> 00:32:07,180
I’ll let you in on a secret.

605
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:10,740
Politically speaking,

606
00:32:13,260 --> 00:32:15,100
I may not be perfect

607
00:32:16,940 --> 00:32:18,220
but I don’t owe anyone.

608
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:24,260
Throughout my life,

609
00:32:25,580 --> 00:32:27,260
I only owe one person,

610
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:32,780
and that is your grandmother.

611
00:32:35,900 --> 00:32:37,660
In every Letter of Introspection,

612
00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:43,660
I’m actually apologizing to her.

613
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:48,140
I beg her

614
00:32:50,220 --> 00:32:52,100
to punish me alone.

615
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:55,500
Don’t...

616
00:33:01,060 --> 00:33:02,380
punish my children.

617
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,420
Leave you out of it.

618
00:33:15,620 --> 00:33:19,140
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =

619
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:21,220
Darling, are you going to rest?

620
00:33:22,020 --> 00:33:23,100
If not,

621
00:33:23,500 --> 00:33:25,220
let me make you some night snacks.

622
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:31,420
= Wang Gongchen’s Wife Xue Yuhu =

623
00:33:31,481 --> 00:33:31,993
This...

624
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:34,140
This is...

625
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:37,860
This is from Ouyang Xiu’s report

626
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:40,220
who’s with the Remonstrance Bureau.

627
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:43,500
He calls all censors useless

628
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:45,020
and unqualified for their posts.

629
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:48,220
He says censors are incompetent

630
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:51,420
especially these days.

631
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:55,500
Why didn’t he

632
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:57,300
call me incompetent directly?

633
00:33:57,300 --> 00:33:58,580
Then I’d feel better.

634
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:01,220
You were born poor

635
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:03,340
and worked your way up yourself.

636
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:05,500
You passed the exam at 19

637
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:07,220
and was crowned the top scholar by His Majesty.

638
00:34:07,420 --> 00:34:08,780
How could you be incompetent?

639
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:11,900
I bet he’s jealous of you.

640
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:13,740
You two took the exam in the same year

641
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:15,500
but he fell behind you.

642
00:34:16,180 --> 00:34:17,420
He isn’t jealous of me

643
00:34:18,660 --> 00:34:19,780
but simply despises me.

644
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:22,060
He looks down on my family background

645
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:23,580
and my literary talent.

646
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:25,300
I know

647
00:34:25,700 --> 00:34:28,460
Ouyang Xiu is the leader of the literary circle.

648
00:34:28,460 --> 00:34:29,460
Before the exam,

649
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,740
I never expected to be on the top,

650
00:34:31,260 --> 00:34:32,860
but His Majesty picked me.

651
00:34:33,380 --> 00:34:35,740
I knew I wasn’t the most talented,

652
00:34:35,860 --> 00:34:37,020
so I bowed to His Majesty and said

653
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:39,100
I happened to have done the exam essay before.

654
00:34:39,340 --> 00:34:40,140
His Majesty told me

655
00:34:40,140 --> 00:34:42,260
he appreciated the spirit between the lines.

656
00:34:43,660 --> 00:34:46,380
That’s why my father likes you.

657
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:48,300
I remember he said

658
00:34:48,660 --> 00:34:50,540
talents may be few

659
00:34:50,660 --> 00:34:52,940
but the honest ones are fewer.

660
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:55,780
But Ouyang Xiu and the others

661
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:58,100
suspected that I pandered to Prime Minister Lv

662
00:34:58,100 --> 00:34:59,340
to get the essay question in advance.

663
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:01,300
They belittled my ability.

664
00:35:01,740 --> 00:35:02,540
Fine.

665
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:04,180
They doubted my personality.

666
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:05,740
I know what kind of person I am.

667
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:07,700
Your sister’s death

668
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:09,060
broke my heart

669
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:10,900
but I couldn’t turn down your father’s request.

670
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:12,700
Yet Ouyang Xiu made fun of me

671
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:14,060
and even wrote poems to mock me.

672
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,460
A while ago,

673
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:18,340
ever His Majesty and the princess

674
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:20,620
saw and heard about it.

675
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:21,980
I became a laughing stock

676
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:24,220
in the entire city.

677
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:33,020
I suffered all that in silence,

678
00:35:33,700 --> 00:35:35,460
but now, he’s targeting

679
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:36,540
at my job.

680
00:35:37,380 --> 00:35:40,180
He said all censors

681
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,820
are incompetent,

682
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:43,900
especially these days.

683
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:45,420
Especially these days!

684
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:47,140
Ouyang Xiu,

685
00:35:47,140 --> 00:35:49,460
how dare you!

686
00:36:15,140 --> 00:36:15,900
Your Majesty.

687
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:17,380
Go get Ren Shouzhong for me.

688
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:39,260
= Yan Mansion =

689
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:47,140
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =

690
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:51,140
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo =

691
00:36:52,100 --> 00:36:53,580
Prime Minister Yan, you’re my teacher.

692
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:55,540
I wouldn’t have come this far without you.

693
00:36:56,700 --> 00:36:58,140
= Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =
I shouldn’t have done this.

694
00:36:58,140 --> 00:37:00,900
Scholar Ouyang, His Majesty selected you himself.

695
00:37:01,500 --> 00:37:03,780
I don’t regard myself as your teacher.

696
00:37:04,540 --> 00:37:06,260
We’re simply colleagues.

697
00:37:08,740 --> 00:37:11,140
You’re always sharp.

698
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:14,060
You criticize everything and everyone

699
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:16,100
that you find inappropriate without mercy.

700
00:37:16,980 --> 00:37:18,220
Officials you haven’t offended

701
00:37:18,220 --> 00:37:20,220
can be counted with one hand.

702
00:37:21,260 --> 00:37:24,940
You embarrassed the Censorate with a few words.

703
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:27,580
That’s fierce!

704
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:31,740
All I said is true.

705
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:33,700
There’s no fabrication.

706
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:36,460
I’m sorry if others feel offended,

707
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:39,340
but it has to be done.

708
00:37:45,460 --> 00:37:48,740
You said all censors are incompetent.

709
00:37:49,540 --> 00:37:51,260
Whether it’s true or not

710
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:53,700
depends on

711
00:37:53,700 --> 00:37:54,700
where you set the bar.

712
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:57,260
If the bar is set too high to be met,

713
00:37:57,420 --> 00:37:59,500
of course you can say they’re incapable

714
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,620
and incompetent.

715
00:38:00,940 --> 00:38:02,380
Seeing how demanding you are,

716
00:38:02,740 --> 00:38:04,220
officials will automatically assume

717
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:06,980
the reform you support is of the same style.

718
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,180
Will harsh criticism

719
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:10,500
induce improvement?

720
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:12,860
If the Censorate can be grilled,

721
00:38:12,900 --> 00:38:15,300
then so can other administrative branches.

722
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:17,780
Generals who lost to Yuanhao

723
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:18,700
are incompetent.

724
00:38:19,260 --> 00:38:20,860
Officials who failed to stop the floods

725
00:38:20,860 --> 00:38:21,820
are incompetent.

726
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:23,420
Astrologers unable to predict heavy snows

727
00:38:23,420 --> 00:38:24,900
are incompetent.

728
00:38:26,340 --> 00:38:27,620
They all have flaws.

729
00:38:28,020 --> 00:38:29,300
When stopped by the river,

730
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:31,500
one would feel inferior to fish.

731
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:32,460
Unable to swim is his flaw.

732
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:33,660
When blocked by the mountain,

733
00:38:33,660 --> 00:38:34,940
one would feel inferior to a bird.

734
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:35,980
Unable to fly is his flaw.

735
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:38,260
Like that, everyone is flawed.

736
00:38:38,380 --> 00:38:41,020
You could say you told the truth

737
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:42,860
but you had no solutions.

738
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:45,300
The Remonstrance Bureau criticized the Censorate

739
00:38:45,700 --> 00:38:49,980
who will then nitpick about military affairs.

740
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:56,500
After arriving in Binzhou,

741
00:38:56,780 --> 00:38:57,980
Yan Du checked Teng Zongliang’s accounts

742
00:38:57,980 --> 00:38:59,260
in Qing County first.

743
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:01,740
All clear. There was no sign of embezzlement.

744
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:04,300
But he found records of money

745
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:06,540
rewarded to some generals and officials.

746
00:39:06,620 --> 00:39:08,620
So he arrested them all

747
00:39:08,740 --> 00:39:10,220
for interrogation.

748
00:39:11,100 --> 00:39:12,580
Every cell in Binzhou

749
00:39:12,580 --> 00:39:13,540
was occupied.

750
00:39:14,740 --> 00:39:16,540
When nothing was found, he tortured them.

751
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:19,180
They cracked and listed names they could think of,

752
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:20,900
including Chong Shiheng

753
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:22,940
and Di Qing.

754
00:39:28,060 --> 00:39:29,620
Your finding is spot-on.

755
00:39:31,180 --> 00:39:34,540
I annoyed the entire Censorate,

756
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:37,420
so they hold grudges against me.

757
00:39:38,900 --> 00:39:39,980
I’m always close

758
00:39:40,260 --> 00:39:43,420
to Fan Zhongyan, Han Qi and Fu Bi.

759
00:39:44,300 --> 00:39:45,660
We’re like-minded.

760
00:39:45,660 --> 00:39:47,900
So they regard us as a clique

761
00:39:48,660 --> 00:39:50,300
and now, they’re after officials

762
00:39:50,420 --> 00:39:51,900
promoted

763
00:39:52,020 --> 00:39:54,300
and appreciated by us.

764
00:39:57,660 --> 00:39:59,020
Prime Minister Yan, given what you said,

765
00:40:00,060 --> 00:40:02,860
please uphold justice

766
00:40:03,380 --> 00:40:05,300
and clear Teng Zongliang’s name.

767
00:40:06,980 --> 00:40:09,180
Yongshu, be cautious.

768
00:40:10,580 --> 00:40:13,740
Gentlemen are bonded by the belief their share

769
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,500
while the corrupted

770
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:16,580
gather together for profits.

771
00:40:17,220 --> 00:40:18,380
Even if we’re a clique,

772
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:21,380
it’s a clique of gentlemen.

773
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:23,620
I’m proud of it.

774
00:40:24,740 --> 00:40:27,020
Forming cliques is strictly prohibited.

775
00:40:27,980 --> 00:40:30,700
As a member of the Cabinet

776
00:40:30,700 --> 00:40:32,180
and the Privy Council,

777
00:40:33,140 --> 00:40:34,620
I cannot get involved in it.

778
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:38,060
I’ll report everything

779
00:40:39,140 --> 00:40:41,180
about our conversation today

780
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:44,020
to His Majesty before the court discussion.

781
00:40:44,380 --> 00:40:45,220
Thank you, teacher.

782
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:07,860
Obviously,

783
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:12,220
even if they’re dedicated officials,

784
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:13,500
no one

785
00:41:13,500 --> 00:41:15,500
can be completely selfless and fair.

786
00:41:17,140 --> 00:41:19,380
Birds of a feather flock together.

787
00:41:19,380 --> 00:41:21,500
It’s inevitable

788
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:23,220
that rival factions will be formed.

789
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:29,420
The after-effect has already surfaced.

790
00:41:46,340 --> 00:41:47,260
You’re...

791
00:41:48,580 --> 00:41:49,420
Sir.

792
00:41:52,380 --> 00:41:53,460
Hanchen?

793
00:41:57,340 --> 00:41:58,980
What happened at the border

794
00:41:59,140 --> 00:42:00,500
that you came all the way to the Capital?

795
00:42:01,540 --> 00:42:03,820
I came in secret to meet with you.

796
00:42:11,740 --> 00:42:15,580
Yan Du’s investigation also includes you.

797
00:42:16,260 --> 00:42:17,100
Did he...

798
00:42:17,700 --> 00:42:19,340
He wouldn’t dare to arrest me.

799
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:20,820
I can assure you

800
00:42:20,980 --> 00:42:22,180
that I’m not a fugitive.

801
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:24,100
And I wouldn’t travel

802
00:42:24,100 --> 00:42:25,380
for two days and nights

803
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:27,140
to get to the city without approval

804
00:42:27,260 --> 00:42:28,300
only to defend myself.

805
00:42:31,060 --> 00:42:32,220
Then why are you...

806
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:45,180
I’m here for Shuiluo City.

807
00:42:46,540 --> 00:42:49,980
It’s more important than anyone.

808
